Name: Invoke: Javelin II
Desc:
Enhances Invoke: Javelin. When Invoke: Javelin hits an enemy, it splits into smaller fragments to perform additional attacks.
It can be linked with Craft: Orb II and it is not affected by skill enhancement effects for multi-target skills. Javelin and Magic Missile prioritize tracking Boss Monsters with the highest Max HP.
Required Skill: Invoke: Javelin Level 20,Bless Mark Mastery Level 10
